{"title":"思念","authors":["佩雷斯"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":3,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佩雷斯［阿根廷］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，你在远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我很想见到你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上那伟大的长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北京走到西藏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，你在远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我渴望见到你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看勤劳的亿万人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样把悠久古国建设得更加辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，你在远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我能够感觉到你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出双手能把你抚摸到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为你就在我的心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（顾丽华　译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}